name: Kelly Daniel
description: A little bit about me? Well, I strongly believe that I am a simple kinda woman with a good sense of humor. I consider myself very friendly, open minded, compassionate, sincere, truthful and honest.First and foremost I’m looking for a very good friend and hopefully the friendship will ultimately lead to a more serious relationship as I’m definitely ready to move on to the next chapter in my life. I’m looking for someone who is very motivated, driven and ambitious, someone I can share my good and bad days with and vice versa.
